lyrics:
[verse]
Hot dogs sizzling on the grill, oh so fine
Gin tonics flowing, we're feeling just fine
The party's jumping, everybody's here
Dancing to the rhythm, full of cheer

[chorus]
Polka trap, hot dogs and gin tonics
We're twisting, turning, getting hypnotic
Polka trap, the energy's so electric
Raise your glass, let's celebrate and get hectic
